2	 * Provider adapter interface.
3	 *
4	 * Every provider-native adapter (Anthropic, Vertex Gemini, OpenAI) must
5	 * implement this interface. The OracleAIClient dispatches through it; no
6	 * route handler or worker may call the provider SDKs directly.
